title: Week 8 preview & Chargers vs. Broncos recap
itunes:title: Week 8 preview & Chargers vs. Broncos recap
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- preview every game on the Week 8 NFL schedule and recap the Broncos' win against the Chargers on TNF.
